WEBVTT

00:00:17.104 --> 00:00:22.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When a man
becomes a father

00:00:22.145 --> 00:00:27.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And a woman
has a child of her own,

00:00:27.270 --> 00:00:33.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They share a trust,
they must remember,

00:00:33.020 --> 00:00:38.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That is not theirs,
not theirs alone.

00:00:38.770 --> 00:00:44.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The gift they share
is from Jehovah;

00:00:44.187 --> 00:00:49.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Of life and love
he is the one true Source.

00:00:49.937 --> 00:00:55.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To parents
he gives sure direction

00:00:55.437 --> 00:01:00.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That they may follow
the wisest course.

00:01:00.687 --> 00:01:06.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A sacred trust
you have been given;

00:01:06.395 --> 00:01:11.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A precious life
is in your hands.

00:01:11.729 --> 00:01:17.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You can bestow
the greatest favor;

00:01:17.770 --> 00:01:23.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Instruct your child
in God’s commands.

00:01:31.687 --> 00:01:37.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All the words
God has commanded—

00:01:37.020 --> 00:01:42.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They must always prove
to be on your heart.

00:01:42.104 --> 00:01:48.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
These words you’ll speak
to sons and daughters;

00:01:48.229 --> 00:01:53.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is your trust,
this is your part.

00:01:53.562 --> 00:01:59.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To them you’ll speak
along your roadway,

00:01:59.104 --> 00:02:04.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When you rise up
and when you are at rest.

00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:10.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In years to come,
may they remember,

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:15.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May they be faithful,
may they be blessed.

00:02:15.812 --> 00:02:21.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A sacred trust
you have been given;

00:02:21.479 --> 00:02:26.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A precious life
is in your hands.

00:02:26.645 --> 00:02:32.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You can bestow
the greatest favor;

00:02:32.770 --> 00:02:42.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Instruct your child
in God’s commands.

